components.label: Building Category
components.description:
Part 3 are simple buildings (eg. single family home).
Part 9 are complex buildings (eg. shopping mall).

Building requirements for each type of building are based on the differences in their size and use. While there are no hard and fastrules about the types of buildings in each category, each has general characteristics.
